<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="az">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sual Səhifəsi</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f9;
        }

        .container {
            padding: 20px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        .question {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 600px;
        }

        .options {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 15px;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 300px;
        }

        .option {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 5px;
            background-color: #fff;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
            text-align: left;
        }

            .option:hover {
                background-color: #ddd;
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="question">Bu, nümunə bir sualdır. Sizcə doğru cavab hansıdır?</div>
        <div class="options">
            <div class="option">A. ......</div>
            <div class="option">B. ......</div>
            <div class="option">C. ......</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
